			<h4><a id="comment_link_44967375" name="comment_link_44967375" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=4270513&amp;cid=44967375" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(44967375)" >We're in a major hurricane "drought"</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_44967375" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 44967375); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
