		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_44967375"><p>Since Wilma, there have been no major hurricanes which have made landfall on the  US mainland.  Zero.  Sandy was not a "major hurricane"; it did a lot of damage because of where it hit, but it was still only Category 1 in strength.  This is the longest major hurricane drought on record.</p></div>
	</div>

